				<tr> <td>This notice contains important information about your rights and responsibilities under the Fair Credit Billing Act.<br/><br/></td></tr>
				<tr> <td style="text-align: left;font-weight:bold;">NOTIFY US IN CASE OF ERRORS OR QUESTIONS ABOUT YOUR INVOICE OR STATEMENT.</td></tr>
